Package: primedtools
Version: 0.1.0
Type: Package
Title: Tools for PRIMED Benchmarking Workflows
Description: Functions for running PRIMED PGS (Polygenic Score) pipeline
    workflows in an AnVIL workspace. Includes tools for fetching scores from
    the PGS Catalog and calculating PGS on cohort genotype data using the
    GCPAnVIL Bioconductor package.
Author: PRIMED Consortium
Maintainer: PRIMED Consortium <primed@uw.edu>
Depends:
    R (>= 4.0.0)
Imports:
    AnVIL,
    dplyr,
    janitor,
    methods,
    purrr,
    readr,
    stringr,
    tidyr,
    utils
Suggests:
    roxygen2,
    testthat,
    mockery
